WEBVTT

00:09:58.379 --> 00:10:00.929
I made the right decision.

00:10:01.397 --> 00:10:04.418
The first day I walked into the school,

00:10:04.442 --> 00:10:08.806
I saw all these little Shameems
staring back at me --

00:10:08.830 --> 00:10:10.163
(Laughter)

00:10:10.187 --> 00:10:12.903
with dreams in their eyes,

00:10:12.927 --> 00:10:16.635
the same dream of freedom
which I had in my childhood.

00:10:17.640 --> 00:10:21.973
So the girls are eager to learn,
but the school is understaffed.

00:10:22.771 --> 00:10:26.484
Girls sit hopeful,

00:10:26.508 --> 00:10:27.662
learn nothing,

00:10:27.686 --> 00:10:28.844
and they leave.

00:10:28.868 --> 00:10:31.670
I can't bear to see this happening.